\mathrm{Var}(\bar{x}) = \frac{1}{n^2} \sum_i \mathrm{Var}(x_i) =  \frac{1}{n^2} \cdot n = \frac{1}{n}
\mathcal{I}(\mu) = \frac{1}{\mathrm{Var}(\bar{x})} = n
